Just a reminder to everyone: tomorrow is the last day to get your 
char numbers within char limits. If you have more than 7 bots per 
faction, you need to cut it down to 7, and if you have over 16 chars 
after tomorrow, you'll need to post for each of them at least every 
other day, or terrible things will happen.
